title: 15-Love 01-03 (2011|Digital|AnPymGold-Empire)
description:
Promotional info for the collected edition - "Teenage tennis action as only Mighty Marvel can deliver! Tennis is Mill Collins' whole life. But as the lowest-ranking student at the Wayde Tennis Academy, she's about to lose her scholarship - and any chance at reaching her dream. Her coach has given up on her, her aunt thinks she doesn't try, and the only one who believes in her is a washed-up drunk. How wrong can things possibly go before Mill catches a break?"

Written by Andi Watson with art from Tommy Ohtsuka. All copies are digital by AnPymGold-Empire. Thanks to them for their efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
